headline: Dell (DELL) Stock Trades Down, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of computer hardware and IT solutions company Dell (NYSE:DELL) fell 4.2% in the morning session after the company admitted at the CES 2026 tech conference that its push for artificial intelligence in personal computers was not resonating with customers.

headline: Is It Time To Revisit Dell Technologies (DELL) After Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: If you are wondering whether Dell Technologies' share price still reflects good value after a strong multi year run, this article will walk through what the numbers are saying right now. The stock closed at US$120.07, with returns of 213.5% over 3 years and 263.5% over 5 years, while the last 30 days show a 14.5% decline and the year to date return sits at a 6% decline.
